pan></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Is there a time I ca=
n contact you this week by phone to finalize your contents claim? the loss s=
chedule provided by Asset Restore to date exceeds your sum insured, which me=
ans that the contents is a total
 loss as the total value of the contents damaged or destroyed is greater the=
n the sum insured. I work until 1:30 so let me know when this week suits you=
.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
